{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"be559f93ef","title":"文化革命是触及人们灵魂的革命","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"55c57b8178","index":0,"year":1966,"month":4,"day":22,"articleId":"be559f93ef","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"重要党内斗争和案件","id":"83b1479e48","type":"主题"},{"name":"指导理论","id":"c1c0033e04","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"e2305b9e63","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"09f9f52b3e","type":"title","text":"文化革命是触及人们灵魂的革命","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"be559f93ef","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b073385314","type":"paragraph","text":"文化革命是触及人们灵魂的革命","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"be559f93ef","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6cb3bae783","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"be559f93ef","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"de277d3734","type":"paragraph","text":"1966.04.22","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"be559f93ef","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4a73278cef","type":"paragraph","text":"我不相信，在文化革命中的问题只是吴晗问题，后面还有一串串“三家村”。文化革命是触及人们灵魂的革命，是意识形态的斗争，触及的很广泛，涉及面很宽。朝里有人，比如中央宣传部、中央文化部都发生这方面的问题，朝里都有人。各大区、各省市都有。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"be559f93ef","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"57f19b0c22","type":"paragraph","text":"在党中央各部门，包括大区、各省市，朝里是否那么干净？我不相信。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"be559f93ef","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}